data.description: Unique opportunity to own this well loved and newly renovated 3 bedroom/2 bath home. Located in the desirable neighborhood of Central Park, you'll enjoy everything this area has to offer such as parks, walking trails, a lake, and near tons of shops, entertainment, and restaurants. This home features NEW luxury vinyl plank flooring, NEW carpet in bedrooms, the roof is less than 2 years old, NEW fence, and the best part is its turn key and MOVE IN READY!!! Bonus points for the shed in the back yard and floored attic space for plenty of extra storage! Purchase this one quick before it's gone!
